Um

00:06:27.580 --> 00:06:31.080
But, uh, the last thing I'll say before I sign off here is the, uh,

00:06:31.760 --> 00:06:34.060
Uh, about the first episode is the...

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:37.660
You know, I was talking about the designs. I love the animals in this.

