Instead of getting up using his legs or, you know, or whatever, standing up,

00:07:15.700 --> 00:07:18.940
he can just use his power, the wind power just to sort of...

00:07:19.260 --> 00:07:20.260
have the wind push him up.

00:07:20.260 --> 00:07:22.020
I love little touches like that.

00:07:22.020 --> 00:07:23.700
