00:07:23.700 --> 00:07:27.480
and she accidentally bends the water, uh, behind her and cracks it,

00:07:27.660 --> 00:07:29.060
and isn't even aware she does it.

00:07:29.060 --> 00:07:31.300
Little things like that, those are great touches.

00:07:31.300 --> 00:07:35.280
